.Dt ipc_bind 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm ipc_bind
.Nd register a service within the IPC namespace
.Sh LIBRARY
libipc, -lipc
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In ipc.h
.Ft int
.Fo ipc_bind
.Fa "int domain"
.Fa "const char *service"
.Fa "int version"
.Fc
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Fn ipc_bind
function registers a service name in the IPC namespace.
.Sh RETURN VALUES
.Rv -std
